Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑似机动战士移动体 仍在接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 30秒后就会与本舰接触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对空炮火 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放它们跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我使用多兹步枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中的话 只要一枪就能干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间绰绰有余
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要慌张 按照工作人员的指示行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵引用缆绳第150号 确认连接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制电缆如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边不搞定 核心就动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}开始最终确认引擎功率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}距离诺拉完全瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs52}只剩不到40分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然是歌姬号的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总司令部的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的攻击还在继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达在交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲利特吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有信任已击落两台敌机的菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能让他去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疏散全部居民的时间只剩不到30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功概率一半对一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,概率之类没有意义！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续严密警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各班进行备战 同时继续作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又确认两台敌机？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号上没杰诺亚斯剩下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能够出击的机体 一台也没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能指望高达了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃 看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急 菲利特应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来 它也有固定的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 击毁机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一套啊 那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绷紧神经 还在作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离诺拉瓦解还有几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,32分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让高达把剩下一台…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉内部发现机影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才的那一台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星内部？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主动钻进要瓦解的卫星里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 如果从内部打击卫星轴心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让高达去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 听得见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的机动战士型 入侵诺拉内部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往追击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民的疏散还未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙 还有一台…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达向诺拉内部移动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 入侵机体行动迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给高达送去更强的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE构筑器不是可以现场造吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有数据造不出有效对付敌人的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论武器多强力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用它的是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后定胜负的是人的智慧与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智慧与勇气？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信菲利特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和高达一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业从第五阶段向第六阶段转移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 终于到最后收尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士型吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与阿林斯顿基地失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像遭到了袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是轴心而是基地被攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道轴心分离必须在基地进行？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎司令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想再为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离诺拉完全瓦解 还有20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地状况还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认诺拉全部居民往轴心的避难完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号与轴心的连接进程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现时点为82%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算连接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法与卫星本体分离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地直通线路？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续作业！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的异星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见识见识我们的骨气吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作太快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 上方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不会马上再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 旧警察管理中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本在卫星建成时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该被封闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 您的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里可以完成分离工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好在为了不时之需
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先做过运行准备 现在派用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果这里也被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就真的束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎司令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士型那边就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉外部 第84区附近交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让敌人察觉我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引住敌人就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离诺拉完全瓦解 还有11分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一晃七年过去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 收留你并非因为怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野家族在建造机动战士方面的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我感兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须活出父亲和母亲的那份精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去 传承明日野家族的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我制造的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是与威胁人类和平的邪恶战斗的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是保护人类的 救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士是救世主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你活到现在是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 左下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 右边是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认第一主旋转轴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是第二主旋转轴 分离完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离完全瓦解 还有8分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查控制电缆连接状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星轴心 等离子推进炉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高密度点火准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认全部旋转轴分离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 轴心等离子推进炉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高密度点火！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号  拽航速度前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制轴心姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轴心在被抽离 赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步枪只剩一发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想往前去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不让你再伤害卫星上的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离诺拉完全瓦解 不到3分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉强强赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星内发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一根分离的旋转轴砸在轴心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻挡了运行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能甩掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 蛮干的话 姿态会失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼看就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轴心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离诺拉完全瓦解 不到120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星内还有移动的热源体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得见吗 菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好…作战成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你造的高达果然了得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你立即返回歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被瓦解牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…我不会见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起救我一个 优先拯救更多的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得力量的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着肩负更多的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 保护人类的救世主的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为救世主 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和高达 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认障碍清除！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与联邦军总司令部取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援舰队约10小时内赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 安排留在舰内的平民尽快转移
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须出发前往执行其他任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2小时后 歌姬号将前往法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰正处于作战行动中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式乘员以外的搭乘人员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请迅速移动前往卫星轴心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴能帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会 见面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗的味道吗
